{"tid":1828082,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［TVB日任］17/1 Blackmores X 陳豪 按此領取任務","createTime":"2020-01-17T13:18:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T00:05:57.000Z","uid":75759,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"8104d521813e848e3132212849d572698e25c908","tid":1828082,"uid":75759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T13:18:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">留言無必要有威嚇成份<br />\n記住<span style=\"color: red;\">表達客戶意見係我地個權利</span><br />\n不被捕係大原則</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">記得bookmark: <br />\nTVB廣告商永久抵制名單！！</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD[/size=]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2P7cPeD%5B%2Fsize%3D%5D&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKK%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=6cab4a58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD[/size=]</a></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">[size=5]<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未來方向：</span></span><br />\n聯絡各大黃色經濟APP，擺TVB廣告商上去，方便大家</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">【永久抵制精選@17 Jan 2020】</span></span></strong><br />\n1.派嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 2.請願<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 3.推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 4.永久抵制 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5. 互like留言，推上FB留言熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">Blackmores X 陳豪</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NE7NUFk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNE7NUFk.jpg&h=e485521f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n👇🏻😡去Blackmores 專頁派嬲兼留言！👇🏻<br />\n<a href=\"https://facebook.com/blackmoreshk/posts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2Fblackmoreshk%2Fposts&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKK%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=c5c71d0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://facebook.com/blackmoreshk/posts</a><br />\n<br />\n👇🏻😢去陳豪Facebook 勸佢離開TVB！👇🏻<br />\n2️⃣ <a href=\"https://facebook.com/coffeemoses/posts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2Fcoffeemoses%2Fposts&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKK%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=9dc8d3f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://facebook.com/coffeemoses/posts</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">※留言template</span></span></strong><br />\n<blockquote>抵制TVB運動已開始半年，貴公司仍然用無綫電視藝人作代言實屬不智，本人深表遺憾，並呼籲貴公司停止與無綫藝人合作，否則將永久抵制貴公司，敬請注意。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">講下臭屎</span></span></strong> <br />\n<blockquote>Blackmores 搵曾經喺澳洲留學嘅TVB偽人陳豪代言無非都係想標榜自己係澳洲品牌。🇦🇺<br />\n但係2018年《太陽先驅報》曾經揭發呢個維他命品牌用嘅<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">原材料係嚟自中國</span></strong>🇨🇳！😳<br />\n都話TVB廣告客戶都係唔多老實啦！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n歡迎用呢幅圖留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CeBV3wt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCeBV3wt.jpg&h=08f539fa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y8o5Gh8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy8o5Gh8.jpg&h=82f3a515&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2PAGY4P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2PAGY4P.png&h=5c5e33c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">記得bookmark<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: TVB廣告客戶名單！！</span></strong> </span><br />\n消費前諗清楚 <br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2P7cPeD&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKK%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=756df161\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD</a> <br />\n週街貼文宣圖：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Mc2yKv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Mc2yKv&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKK%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=fad07ed8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2Mc2yKv</a><br />\n－－－－－－－ <br />\n請即follow:<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"http://www.fb.com/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fb.com%2Fsayno2tvb&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKK%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=6cfebc06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.fb.com/sayno2tvb</a><br />\nTelegram: <a href=\"http://t.me/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno2tvb&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKK%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=26e6c6d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/sayno2tvb</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fsayno2tvb&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKK%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=6fe39c17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.instagram.com/sayno2tvb</a><br />\n<br />\n繼續狙擊CCTVB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n以下為最新笑料<br />\n<del><strong>愛回家偽人表示五大訴求缺一不可</strong></del><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pYTpWUS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpYTpWUS.jpg&h=483564a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實係廣告時段播足全首劇集主題曲攝時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nTVB你無嘢播不如播吓心穎的士大戰Broken Man算啦<br />\n一定大把師奶熄機 創造收視奇蹟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"